 Amazing Facts Media Library - https://www.amazingfacts.org/media-library

Since its inception more than 50 years ago, Amazing Facts has brought the gospel to millions around the worldand multitudes have found new life in Christ. In the last few years, Amazing Facts has grown explosively under Gods blessing, but for the ministry to reach even more people for Christ, we need a new home. Our current facilities can no longer accommodate our people or our programs. Recognizing that time is running short on Planet Earth, we are embarking on a bold plan to redeem more people by building the World Outreach, Revival, and Discipleship Centerthe W.O.R.D. Center.

Please join Pastor Doug and Amazing Facts in this incredible end-time opportunity. Learn more at afwordcenter.org.
